snippet.title: Tutorial: Amber Heard Braided Hairstyle
snippet.description:
A quick and easy tutorial to get Amber Heard's braided red carpet hairstyle.

Products used:
Fab Remy Clip in hair extensions (our model uses 20" in colour 12/16/613) - http://bit.ly/1Cwtbzg

Tigi Bed Head Oh Bee Hive Matte Dry Shampoo - http://bit.ly/19C326V

To curl the hair we used the Babyliss Pro Curling Tong (38mm) - http://bit.ly/1I1fSXK
